text:
Good job, Mano.
You managed the first day well.

Well...
...but I'm a little nervous about what's going to happen.

What's wrong?
If there's something bothering you, please tell me.

Well... I'm a bit anxious about the joint training camp
with the other units. What if I can't keep up?

I see... But I don't think you need to worry so much.
Remember, the members of the other units are not strangers.
While it's important to adapt to others to some extent...
You'll be fine, Mano. I believe in you.

Yes, you're right.
I'm sorry for causing you worry.
I need to do my best too... Mmhn.
